Keep up the healthy lifestyle.
Try to drink as many as eight cups of water per day.
Know your limits, then push them!
Remember, everything in moderation!
Consider taking brisk walks in the morning.
Running is great way to stay in shape.
Weight training is a good way to burn fat.
Add more vegetables to your diet.
Try cutting the amount of fast-meals you consume.
Avoid processed foods that have high sodium and sugar counts.
